Title: Logotyrapy
Description:
Dear $n,

It seems almost wrong to say, but I am worried about Tyr. When he arrived at Tyr's Rest, he spent many days talking with us. We all asked him many questions, learning about the titans, ancient history, and what it means to be good.

But recently, Tyr has been speaking less, and the answers he does give are shorter and some have an edge to them.

I'm not sure what's wrong, but something is different. Will you come speak with him?

For Tyr,
Valunei
